{"tid":1776685,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天盛苑法團戰後繼 (文長注意) 法團儲備清空大計劃","createTime":"2019-12-09T16:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T07:22:51.000Z","uid":120355,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"533d49c99b1793a8189abb8f0819e118a1418f51","tid":1776685,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"天水圍天盛苑業主大會 12月3日 被民主陣線成員甘天成(天盛業委主席)恐嚇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1760285\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1760285</a><br />\n天盛12月3罷業法團大會 出現咗1張票=700户業主嘅荒謬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767932\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767932</a><br />\n<br />\n咁好啦<br />\n再講下12月3號之後發生既事啦<br />\n<br />\n當晚就總共有27.3%既業主出席<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mskqFG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmskqFG8.jpg&h=70b44f34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點算結果<br />\n贊成 業權份數 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">55677</span></span></strong><br />\n反對 業權份數 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">68374</span></span></strong><br />\n有一張反對票 業權份數<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">44037</span></span></strong><br />\n總業權份數為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">124051</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁其實27.3% 到底會有幾多業權份數呢?<br />\n以全苑<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>6580戶</strong></span></span>黎計<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">27.3%</span></strong></span><br />\n大約就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1797</span></span></strong>戶 <br />\n天盛細單位-大單位份數比值為<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">39-60</span></span></strong><br />\n我以全部大單位黎計呢就只係得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">107820</span></span></strong>份數<br />\n同總數有出入 多左萬幾份數<br />\n之後街坊不滿 要求解釋 <br />\n啟勝話隔日會解釋<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">並且封箱,日後再點票</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好啦隔左幾日出左份咁既通告<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PkaRVx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PkaRVx.png&h=60976efc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">NANI!?</span><br />\n突然變左<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">35.2%</span></span></strong>出席率<br />\n變成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2316戶</span></span></strong> 有造假之嫌<br />\n而且當時12月3號係封左箱<br />\n從未開過箱同埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">監票人仲未簽名</span></strong></span>既情況下你就出左張咁既通告<br />\n<br />\n好啦<br />\n啟勝同法團蛇鼠一窩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未放棄<br />\n會再搞特別大會</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁法團既攬炒大計已經開始左</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emg9n94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Femg9n94.jpg&h=57c9006f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦呢個免管理費之前講過 唔再多講啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係大家知唔知2018年政府出過一份報告關於更換舊式單制動器既升降機呢 <br />\n<a href=\"https://brplatform.org.hk/tc/subsidy-and-assistance/limss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrplatform.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fsubsidy-and-assistance%2Flimss&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=b91de2d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://brplatform.org.hk/tc/subsidy-and-assistance/limss</a><br />\n無錯 我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天盛就係用單制式</span></span></strong><br />\n到時又要外牆維修更換水管<br />\n呢家又要換升降機<br />\n那有錢_ _ _ <br />\n點換呀????<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天盛區議員情況 :</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n現任區議員狀況: <span style=\"color: blue;\">陳思靜 - 消失 </span><br />\n<br />\n候任區議員狀況:<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 區國權 (天盛屏欣兩苑)</span><br />\n積極了解 多次現身 <br />\n12月3號有出席法團大會並上前了解<br />\n12月6號晚上有到場了解<br />\n<br />\n候任區議員狀況: <span style=\"color: gold;\">侯文健 </span><br />\n12月3號有出法團大會  只係FB出左個POST<br />\n12月4號出現【天水圍和你跑】<br />\n12月7號FB呼籲去維園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案例:淘大花園換電梯 料涉款半億<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2078402/?lcc=at\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2078402%2F%3Flcc%3Dat&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=4f78dcc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2078402/?lcc=at</a><br />\n<br />\n天盛苑那代表700個單位的票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069205&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=b394fbb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069205&h=cd373d53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069205</a><br />\n<br />\n【種票舉報】天盛苑撤換法團大會 居民揭八成反對票為授權票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/406037/%E7%A8%AE%E7%A5%A8%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1-%E5%A4%A9%E7%9B%9B%E8%8B%91%E6%92%A4%E6%8F%9B%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%AD%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8%E7%82%BA%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F406037%2F%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259B%259B%25E8%258B%2591%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=fba3f701\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.co